1	//! Worker Service - Business logic layer for worker operations
2	//!
3	//! This module provides a clean separation between HTTP concerns (in routers)
4	//! and business logic for worker management. The service orchestrates
5	//! WorkerRegistry and JobQueue operations.
6	
